---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout
  title="Privacy Policy – PPC Tool Bench"
  description="Read the privacy policy of PPC Tool Bench to understand how information may be collected, used, and protected on this website."
  currentPath="/privacy"
>
  <main class="card">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      This page explains how PPC Toolbench may collect, use, and protect information
      when you use this website.
    </p>

    <h2>Information we may collect</h2>
    <p>
      We may collect limited technical information such as browser type, device type,
      referring pages, and general usage data to help maintain and improve the website.
    </p>

    <h2>How tool inputs are handled</h2>
    <p>
      The tools on this website are designed to be simple and privacy-conscious.
      We do not intentionally store the URLs or campaign values you enter into client-side tools,
      unless explicitly stated otherwise for a specific feature.
    </p>

    <h2>Analytics and measurement</h2>
    <p>
      We may use website analytics or similar measurement technologies to understand
      general site usage, traffic patterns, and tool performance.
    </p>

    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>
      This website may use cookies or similar technologies for basic functionality,
      analytics, security, and performance purposes.
    </p>

    <h2>Third-party services</h2>
    <p>
      We may rely on third-party service providers such as hosting, analytics,
      or infrastructure providers to operate the site. Those providers may process
      limited technical data as part of delivering their services.
    </p>

    <h2>Advertising</h2>
    <p>
      In the future, this website may display advertising provided by third-party advertising partners.
      Those partners may use cookies or similar technologies in accordance with their own policies
      and applicable legal requirements.
    </p>

    <h2>Data protection</h2>
    <p>
      We take reasonable steps to maintain the security and reliability of the website,
      but no internet transmission or storage method can be guaranteed to be fully secure.
    </p>

    <h2>Policy updates</h2>
    <p>
      This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time to reflect operational,
      legal, or service changes. Please review this page periodically for the latest version.
    </p>
  </main>
</MainLayout>